Miner may do your job for you. It can dig resources (ores). But it requires mining pipes. You have to craft 54 of them. (other 10 will be the reward for you). In total 64 mining pipes are enough to dig all ores above bedrock. But quality of work is depends on height where you will place your miner, to give to its ability to dig all ores above bedrock. For example it can dig all ores on the sea level with one stack (64 items) of mining pipes inside it. Note, that you may give to miner lower (than 8 eu/t) energy to work and it will be ok (but it may works slower). So, when you craft miner and mining pipes, you may place your miner anywhere. Then just put mining pipes inside it, connect it with energy and enjoy. Btw, it may auto output mined ores.
